<hw>Lem*nis"cate</hw>
<pr>(l⟦ecr⟧m*n⟦icr⟧s"k⟦asl⟧t)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>lemniscatus</ets> adorned with ribbons, fr. <ets>lemniscus</ets> a
